<item>
            <title>[LU-14213] enable parallel e2fsck by default</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14213</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be very useful to enable multi-threaded e2fsck for all test runs by default.  This would be best handled by adding an option in &lt;tt&gt;/etc/e2fsck.conf&lt;/tt&gt; so that the default behavior can easily be changed without having to modify the code.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
